README
The Tiny App Project

Tiny App: Annoying Doge
Produced By: Lu Meng

Overview
In this tiny app, you will answer a question asked by Doge. Her response may be different (and annoying) according to your answer. 

Usage Instructions
Answer Doge's Yes/No questions by touching "YES" or "NO" button.

Running Requirements
Android 6.0 (Marshmallow)

Documentation and Resources Used
Android Studio

What did I learn from developing this app?
1. How to build a project in Android Studio;
2. How to add layouts, widgets and images in the project;
3. How to start a new activty on button click;
4. How to build a activity that switchs screens;
5. How to let the app support screens that have different sizes.
